f60ff808b050f1bdee0a3a015724111fed4737","tid":2048641,"uid":2615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T03:20:51.000Z","msg":"叫雞唔沖涼點得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64add12c8b0ae225637e29e0f496e7f6fa005e04","tid":2048641,"uid":27359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T03:29:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.fsis.usda.gov/wps/portal/fsis/topics/food-safety-education/get-answers/food-safety-fact-sheets/safe-food-handling/washing-food-does-it-promote-food-safety/washing-food\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fsis.usda.gov%2Fwps%2Fportal%2Ffsis%2Ftopics%2Ffood-safety-education%2Fget-answers%2Ffood-safety-fact-sheets%2Fsafe-food-handling%2Fwashing-food-does-it-promote-food-safety%2Fwashing-food&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=89151384\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fsis.usda.gov/wps/portal/fsis/topics/food-safety-education/get-answers/food-safety-fact-sheets/safe-food-handling/washing-food-does-it-promote-food-safety/washing-food</a><br />\n<br />\n任何生肉佢都建議唔好洗，佢地特別強調雞肉係因為 1. 美國人好少洗其他肉（豬肉/ 牛肉），2. 雞肉表面特別多菌（沙門氏菌，彎曲桿菌），呢兩隻菌只要好少量已經可以引起食物中毒<br />\n<br />\nUSDA (農業部）咁建議係基於 3 大實驗結果：1. 有啲菌痴係表面痴得好實，你沖洗完會仲有好多菌痴係表面，2. 洗個陣彈出黎嘅水會有菌，仲要飛到好遠，呢啲痴係周圍嘅菌會交叉感染其他嘢，肉眼你睇唔到又唔會清潔到，3. 正常煮食過程已經可以殺晒呢啲菌<br />\n<br />\n所以：唔好洗，肉眼見到嘅污糟野就用手搣走佢。唔好再去街市買污糟大陸肉，買啲靚仔進口雞牛豬肉就唔洗擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389c294e3d85e95d4144e1edb4202339256ba439","tid":2048641,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64add12c8b0ae225637e29e0f496e7f6fa005e04","tid":2048641,"uid":27359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T03:29:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.fsis.usda.gov/wps/portal/fsis/topics/food-safety-education/get-answers/food-safety-fact-sheets/safe-food-handling/washing-food-does-it-promote-food-safety/washing-food\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fsis.usda.gov%2Fwps%2Fportal%2Ffsis%2Ftopics%2Ffood-safety-education%2Fget-answers%2Ffood-safety-fact-sheets%2Fsafe-food-handling%2Fwashing-food-does-it-promote-food-safety%2Fwashing-food&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=89151384\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fsis.usda.gov/wps/portal/fsis/topics/food-safety-education/get-answers/food-safety-fact-sheets/safe-food-handling/washing-food-does-it-promote-food-safety/washing-food</a><br />\n<br />\n任何生肉佢都建議唔好洗，佢地特別強調雞肉係因為 1. 美國人好少洗其他肉（豬肉/ 牛肉），2. 雞肉表面特別多菌（沙門氏菌，彎曲桿菌），呢兩隻菌只要好少量已經可以引起食物中毒<br />\n<br />\nUSDA (農業部）咁建議係基於 3 大實驗結果：1. 有啲菌痴係表面痴得好實，你沖洗完會仲有好多菌痴係表面，2. 洗個陣彈出黎嘅水會有菌，仲要飛到好遠，呢啲痴係周圍嘅菌會交叉感染其他嘢，肉眼你睇唔到又唔會清潔到，3. 正常煮食過程已經可以殺晒呢啲菌<br />\n<br />\n所以：唔好洗，肉眼見到嘅污糟野就用手搣走佢。唔好再去街市買污糟大陸肉，買啲靚仔進口雞牛豬肉就唔洗擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T03:34:42.000Z","msg":"曬氣<br />\n煮食殺晒咁搞咁多做乜春呀<br />\n你煮雞隔離唔會有盒魚生放左係度呀嘛<br />\n<br />\n就算唔洗<br />\n你調味落液體 或者拍打個陣一樣係會飛黎飛去<br />\n落鑊個下油炸已經噴晒啲菌出黎"},{"pid":"fc26435cdb8fa13db8721e8a60ac2b4c59be95ca","tid":2048641,"uid":71218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"747c178d5ce30a362544e3b67b0f67844ac2c3a9","tid":2048641,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aac7dd035e03232ecf918f748ffa7e7a9dd552f1","tid":2048641,"uid":179120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fd54dc3c82007a578e9a096f89055cd7bbeff90","tid":2048641,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T03:06:40.000Z","msg":"美國衛生部之前出咗報告話沖隻雞啲菌會飛到成個廚房都係菌，叫人唔好洗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T03:11:17.000Z","msg":"咁唔揾水喉直接沖，拎個碗浸下咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T03:13:08.000Z","msg":"佢好似就係建議人用水浸，但我自己始終覺得要沖先乾淨<img src=\"/assets/fac